data.name: HostNameTextBox.ToolTip
data.value: The host name to use in place of 'localhost'. This value must be a valid DNS host name or be present in the local hosts file. You may check 'Add hosts entry' to add such an entry to the hosts file for the duration of the hosting session. Adding a hosts entry requires elevated permissions, both upon adding and again upon removal.
